FBU Android Project - TripPin

TripPin is an android app that allows users to share routes and points of interest together. The app utilizes the [Google MAPS API](https://dev.twitter.com/rest/public) for navigation and route creation. 

$$ Usage
Simply clone the repository and build onto your emulator (or phone) using Android Studio.

